00:08:17.260 --> 00:08:22.260
(Risas)

00:08:22.260 --> 00:08:25.260
"Que cousa máis inútil!"

00:08:25.260 --> 00:08:27.260
E eu dígolle: "Non, non, tamén di a data"

00:08:27.260 --> 00:08:31.260
